1
00:00:00,800 --> 00:00:03,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dearest comrades, please respond.</i></font>

2
00:00:05,010 --> 00:00:06,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We have received your mayday.</i></font>

3
00:00:07,300 --> 00:00:11,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We are capable of bringing aboard
all who wish to join us.</i></font>

4
00:00:12,280 --> 00:00:16,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We will be entering stationary orbit 
around your planet soon.</i></font>

5
00:00:17,240 --> 00:00:21,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The specific date and time
according to the global standard time—</i></font>

6
00:01:55,350 --> 00:01:59,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will call rain down 
upon this dry planet.</font>

7
00:01:59,670 --> 00:02:02,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A rain of a thousand immigrant ships.</font>

8
00:02:03,060 --> 00:02:06,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A "Genesis Flood" Big Fall.</font>

9
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:19,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nai, I will stop you.</font>

10
00:02:19,950 --> 00:02:21,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And how are you going to do that?</font>

11
00:02:22,390 --> 00:02:24,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you up and around already?</font>

12
00:02:24,550 --> 00:02:26,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ready as always, better than ever.</font>

13
00:02:26,550 --> 00:02:31,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, if I stayed in bed all the time, 
it'd get the kids worried.</font>

14
00:02:32,210 --> 00:02:33,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So?</font>

15
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:39,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">According to Melanie, Octovern 
was able to repel the Ark's attack.</font>

16
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:42,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're accepting refugees 
from other cities and towns.</font>

17
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Word's gotten out that the city 
will protect people.</font>

18
00:02:48,090 --> 00:02:51,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So Nai will be coming to Octovern.</font>

19
00:02:52,470 --> 00:02:54,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds about right. And?</font>

20
00:02:57,490 --> 00:03:01,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have ideas... about how to stop Nai.</font>

21
00:03:01,650 --> 00:03:03,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's hear them.</font>

22
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:05,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

23
00:03:05,510 --> 00:03:06,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's no good.</font>

24
00:03:07,170 --> 00:03:09,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The town down below is all empty.</font>

25
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:12,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No food, no water, no nothing. 
Just like we figured.</font>

26
00:03:12,940 --> 00:03:14,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a total ghost town.</font>

27
00:03:14,930 --> 00:03:21,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if we seriously cut back, we have 
maybe a week's worth of food and water.</font>

28
00:03:21,340 --> 00:03:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One week...</font>

29
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:26,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And even if we wanted to take refuge 
in Octovern, all the cars are gone.</font>

30
00:03:26,820 --> 00:03:29,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Walking there is out
 of the question, so...</font>

31
00:03:29,210 --> 00:03:32,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Either way, we don't want
 the kids at Octovern.</font>

32
00:03:33,260 --> 00:03:37,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't use the radio either. 
What to do...</font>

33
00:03:39,660 --> 00:03:40,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Home.</font>

34
00:03:40,910 --> 00:03:41,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Home?</font>

35
00:03:41,990 --> 00:03:43,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your house?</font>

36
00:03:44,020 --> 00:03:48,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Luida would accept the kids. 
I'll go ask her myself.</font>

37
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:53,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We could get there in three
 or four days by motorcycle.</font>

38
00:03:53,210 --> 00:03:55,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That sounds like a good idea.</font>

39
00:03:55,900 --> 00:03:59,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But will that leave us enough time
 to deal with Knives?</font>

40
00:03:59,590 --> 00:04:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nai can't do what he wants 
until the immigrant fleet arrives.</font>

41
00:04:04,720 --> 00:04:07,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have enough time
 to visit Home, return here,</font>

42
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:10,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and then make for Octovern... I think.</font>

43
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:13,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds like our only option.</font>

44
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be back before you know it.
 Don't you worry.</font>

45
00:04:18,110 --> 00:04:20,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care out there.</font>

46
00:04:20,070 --> 00:04:21,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm off.</font>

47
00:04:25,900 --> 00:04:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good luck!</font>

48
00:04:33,500 --> 00:04:35,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't drive?! You dumbass!</font>

49
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:38,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?!</font>

50
00:04:46,950 --> 00:04:48,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure about this?</font>

51
00:04:48,980 --> 00:04:50,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I should...</font>

52
00:04:50,660 --> 00:04:54,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, Nico. You're still in rough shape.</font>

53
00:04:54,310 --> 00:04:55,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go.</font>

54
00:04:55,820 --> 00:04:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all good. I know exactly 
where Home is now.</font>

55
00:04:59,460 --> 00:05:00,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

56
00:05:00,590 --> 00:05:02,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Livio.</font>

57
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:03,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need to thank me.</font>

58
00:05:03,950 --> 00:05:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to do what I can for the kids, too.</font>

59
00:05:09,580 --> 00:05:10,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're counting on you.</font>

60
00:05:10,660 --> 00:05:14,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Auntie... Aunt Melanie.</font>

61
00:05:15,740 --> 00:05:17,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I'm off.</font>

62
00:05:29,230 --> 00:05:30,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ouch...</font>

63
00:05:30,810 --> 00:05:32,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! My bones!</font>

64
00:05:33,650 --> 00:05:36,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine, it's fine!
I'll be all fixed up in no time.</font>

65
00:05:40,830 --> 00:05:42,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See? Good as new.</font>

66
00:05:43,020 --> 00:05:45,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And again, I'm off.</font>

67
00:06:03,110 --> 00:06:04,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's it look?</font>

68
00:06:06,060 --> 00:06:10,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been five days. 
He should be back any moment now.</font>

69
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:16,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope he isn't lost in the desert 
or being chased by a pack of Worms.</font>

70
00:06:17,230 --> 00:06:18,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have to trust him and wait.</font>

71
00:06:19,980 --> 00:06:22,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Melanie, how's our food and water?</font>

72
00:06:22,730 --> 00:06:25,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd say two more days left.</font>

73
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

74
00:06:27,290 --> 00:06:30,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right. We're all going to space.</font>

75
00:06:30,700 --> 00:06:33,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A great voyage across the sea of stars!</font>

76
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:37,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll leave this star and find a new one.</font>

77
00:06:37,590 --> 00:06:39,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure we can find a great new home.</font>

78
00:06:39,330 --> 00:06:41,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you coming with us, Nico?</font>

79
00:06:41,690 --> 00:06:43,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I am.</font>

80
00:06:43,170 --> 00:06:44,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Auntie Melanie, too?</font>

81
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:46,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of us together!</font>

82
00:06:46,470 --> 00:06:49,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's travel and eat tons of great food!</font>

83
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:50,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

84
00:06:50,460 --> 00:06:52,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Nico.</font>

85
00:06:52,810 --> 00:06:55,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which way is the spaceship coming from?</font>

86
00:06:55,450 --> 00:06:57,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's...</font>

87
00:06:58,570 --> 00:07:00,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know.</font>

88
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That way? Or maybe that way?</font>

89
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's that direction.</font>

90
00:07:05,770 --> 00:07:07,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you know?</font>

91
00:07:07,820 --> 00:07:10,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the direction of the home star,</font>

92
00:07:10,540 --> 00:07:12,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">where everyone living
on Noman's Land hails from.</font>

93
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:14,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean Earth!</font>

94
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:17,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. So it'll be that way.</font>

95
00:07:17,010 --> 00:07:18,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can we see them?</font>

96
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:20,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way you can see them!</font>

97
00:07:20,530 --> 00:07:22,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, there they are!</font>

98
00:07:22,010 --> 00:07:23,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're lying!</font>

99
00:07:23,510 --> 00:07:27,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not. Look. One, two... Thirty ships!</font>

100
00:07:27,760 --> 00:07:31,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, you're right. Look at that guy 
waving from the window.</font>

101
00:07:31,420 --> 00:07:33,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Where, where?!</font>

102
00:07:35,310 --> 00:07:37,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You tricked me!</font>

103
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:41,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vash, did you come from Earth, too?</font>

104
00:07:41,280 --> 00:07:43,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never been to Earth either.</font>

105
00:07:43,970 --> 00:07:46,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were born aboard a ship in transit.</font>

106
00:07:47,380 --> 00:07:48,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"We"?</font>

107
00:07:48,950 --> 00:07:50,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a twin brother.</font>

108
00:07:50,940 --> 00:07:53,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! Do you have any other family?</font>

109
00:07:56,140 --> 00:07:57,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rem...</font>

110
00:07:57,890 --> 00:08:02,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A woman named Rem Saverem raised us.</font>

111
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:04,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is she your mom?</font>

112
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:07,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, she was like our mom.</font>

113
00:08:08,590 --> 00:08:12,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rem was kind and taught us many things.</font>

114
00:08:13,140 --> 00:08:16,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know. I'll share with you 
something she use to say.</font>

115
00:08:17,170 --> 00:08:19,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen well.</font>

116
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:25,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We all have a blank ticket 
with no listed destination.</font>

117
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:28,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What you put there is up to you.</font>

118
00:08:28,690 --> 00:08:31,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter the darkness you find yourself in,</font>

119
00:08:31,030 --> 00:08:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you'll always have that ticket 
waiting for you to write in where to go.</font>

120
00:08:38,250 --> 00:08:39,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A blank...</font>

121
00:08:39,760 --> 00:08:41,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...ticket?</font>

122
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone, put out a hand.</font>

123
00:08:46,070 --> 00:08:50,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For you, and for you, and for you.</font>

124
00:08:50,460 --> 00:08:52,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You all have a blank ticket.</font>

125
00:08:54,350 --> 00:08:59,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With this, you can go anywhere
and be anything.</font>

126
00:09:00,190 --> 00:09:04,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As long as you have your ticket, 
you can endure any hardship.</font>

127
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just as I have.</font>

128
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:12,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remember to take good care of your ticket.</font>

129
00:09:12,170 --> 00:09:13,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

130
00:09:19,220 --> 00:09:21,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meryl! Hurry, hurry!</font>

131
00:09:23,620 --> 00:09:24,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jessica!</font>

132
00:09:24,580 --> 00:09:26,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meryl, Milly! The motorcycle!</font>

133
00:09:26,910 --> 00:09:28,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We saw it, too!</font>

134
00:09:30,340 --> 00:09:31,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vash?!</font>

135
00:09:30,340 --> 00:09:31,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Undertaker?!</font>

136
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:34,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello.</font>

137
00:09:37,370 --> 00:09:38,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you?</font>

138
00:09:39,070 --> 00:09:41,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do calm yourselves, you three.</font>

139
00:09:41,550 --> 00:09:43,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, of course. Sorry.</font>

140
00:09:43,850 --> 00:09:45,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought for a moment...</font>

141
00:09:45,740 --> 00:09:49,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe Vash or the Undertaker came back.</font>

142
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:52,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They aren't here. But they're safe.</font>

143
00:09:53,740 --> 00:09:55,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're somewhere else right now.</font>

144
00:09:55,950 --> 00:09:59,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're running out of provisions
and in need of help.</font>

145
00:09:59,490 --> 00:10:01,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came here to let you know.</font>

146
00:10:01,180 --> 00:10:05,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It took him five days to get here, 
no rest or sleep.</font>

147
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:07,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You went five days without sleep?!</font>

148
00:10:07,110 --> 00:10:10,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It should have taken me 
only three days, but...</font>

149
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:12,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeehaw!</font>

150
00:10:12,930 --> 00:10:15,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice ride!</font>

151
00:10:15,430 --> 00:10:17,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Take it!</font>

152
00:10:16,020 --> 00:10:17,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, well...</font>

153
00:10:19,430 --> 00:10:23,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no!</font>

154
00:10:39,370 --> 00:10:40,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's reversed?</font>

155
00:10:42,710 --> 00:10:45,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And several other unforeseen issues arose.</font>

156
00:10:45,650 --> 00:10:49,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure of it. 
That's Livio the Doublefang's voice.</font>

157
00:10:49,130 --> 00:10:54,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is he here to kill us? 
It doesn't seem that way.</font>

158
00:10:54,580 --> 00:10:57,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you want the children 
from the Hopeland orphanage</font>

159
00:10:57,270 --> 00:11:00,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to take refuge on this ship, 
is that right?</font>

160
00:11:00,500 --> 00:11:01,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

161
00:11:01,350 --> 00:11:03,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand the situation.</font>

162
00:11:03,260 --> 00:11:04,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then...</font>

163
00:11:04,260 --> 00:11:05,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However,</font>

164
00:11:05,930 --> 00:11:09,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we cannot accept
 the children here at Home.</font>

165
00:11:22,620 --> 00:11:23,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're here!</font>

166
00:11:28,710 --> 00:11:32,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay! Over here!</font>

167
00:11:32,910 --> 00:11:34,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vash!</font>

168
00:11:35,370 --> 00:11:38,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You dummy! I've been so worried!</font>

169
00:11:38,180 --> 00:11:40,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Jessica.</font>

170
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:42,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boy, am I glad you're all right!</font>

171
00:11:42,610 --> 00:11:45,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meryl, Milly... I'm sorry I worried you.</font>

172
00:11:45,510 --> 00:11:46,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really did.</font>

173
00:11:46,850 --> 00:11:49,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You owe us an exclusive interview!</font>

174
00:11:51,700 --> 00:11:53,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Moreover...</font>

175
00:11:53,660 --> 00:11:54,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

176
00:11:56,310 --> 00:11:58,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened to your hair?</font>

177
00:11:58,570 --> 00:12:00,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got a makeover. Looks good, right?</font>

178
00:12:00,810 --> 00:12:03,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so wild of you!</font>

179
00:12:03,530 --> 00:12:08,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I sort of caused him a lot of 
mental stress... of a certain kind.</font>

180
00:12:08,560 --> 00:12:12,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not your fault. Don't even start.</font>

181
00:12:12,750 --> 00:12:15,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure you're all right?</font>

182
00:12:15,340 --> 00:12:18,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. I just almost died for a bit.</font>

183
00:12:18,130 --> 00:12:19,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

184
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:22,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm more or less fine now.</font>

185
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:26,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That "more or less" is dubious.
You have priors.</font>

186
00:12:27,330 --> 00:12:29,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really, I'm fine.</font>

187
00:12:29,580 --> 00:12:30,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Really?</i></font>

188
00:12:30,880 --> 00:12:33,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really, <i>really</i> fine.</font>

189
00:12:33,370 --> 00:12:35,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can we trust you?</font>

190
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:41,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can trust me.</font>

191
00:12:42,420 --> 00:12:47,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't die. I've gotta
 protect these kids.</font>

192
00:12:47,780 --> 00:12:50,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enough already. Yikes.</font>

193
00:12:52,250 --> 00:12:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So?</font>

194
00:12:54,380 --> 00:12:56,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's all this?</font>

195
00:12:57,970 --> 00:13:01,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We wanted you to take in the kids 
from the orphanage.</font>

196
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:05,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you all come here instead?</font>

197
00:13:05,710 --> 00:13:07,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We spoke to Luida, and...</font>

198
00:13:08,800 --> 00:13:13,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We cannot accept
 the children here at Home.</font>

199
00:13:13,180 --> 00:13:14,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But...</font>

200
00:13:14,590 --> 00:13:15,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Luida!</font>

201
00:13:16,190 --> 00:13:18,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's too dangerous.</font>

202
00:13:18,770 --> 00:13:25,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're almost done repairing the engines. 
This ship will fly again soon.</font>

203
00:13:25,010 --> 00:13:28,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We must go and finish 
our fight against Knives.</font>

204
00:13:29,370 --> 00:13:30,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, Livio...</font>

205
00:13:31,050 --> 00:13:33,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We implore you instead.</font>

206
00:13:34,660 --> 00:13:37,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please let the children and 
noncombatants on this ship</font>

207
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:40,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">take refuge in Hopeland.</font>

208
00:13:41,100 --> 00:13:43,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what she said.</font>

209
00:13:43,070 --> 00:13:44,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good call.</font>

210
00:13:44,470 --> 00:13:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Luida for you.</font>

211
00:13:46,250 --> 00:13:50,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We brought lots of food and water, 
so we should be fine for a while.</font>

212
00:13:50,670 --> 00:13:52,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But still...</font>

213
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:54,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you fools doing here?!</font>

214
00:13:54,710 --> 00:14:00,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there a problem? 
We are also noncombatants.</font>

215
00:14:00,220 --> 00:14:04,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The children need their 
music lessons every day.</font>

216
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:05,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

217
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:07,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, kids, it's lesson time.</font>

218
00:14:07,690 --> 00:14:09,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

219
00:14:09,350 --> 00:14:10,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Your Majesty,</font>

220
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:13,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">give us a new puppet show 
after our music lesson, okay?</font>

221
00:14:13,860 --> 00:14:14,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Absolutely not.</font>

222
00:14:14,940 --> 00:14:16,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

223
00:14:14,950 --> 00:14:16,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}All right!</font>

224
00:14:16,540 --> 00:14:17,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I shan't do it.</font>

225
00:14:17,490 --> 00:14:18,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't wait!</font>

226
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:19,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said no.</font>

227
00:14:21,830 --> 00:14:26,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should accompany Vash to Octovern.</font>

228
00:14:26,190 --> 00:14:26,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

229
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:30,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will observe and record 
everything to the bitter end.</font>

230
00:14:28,270 --> 00:14:29,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yes.</font>

231
00:14:31,450 --> 00:14:35,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">History will know how we upheld 
our pride as journalists.</font>

232
00:14:38,870 --> 00:14:39,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yes!</font>

233
00:14:38,870 --> 00:14:43,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, everything's ready. 
Batteries are full, too.</font>

234
00:14:43,780 --> 00:14:46,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can go anywhere now.</font>

235
00:14:48,020 --> 00:14:49,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milly?</font>

236
00:14:50,640 --> 00:14:51,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

237
00:14:55,170 --> 00:14:58,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-Milly, Worm! There's— You're— Worm!</font>

238
00:14:58,280 --> 00:15:00,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'm so glad!</font>

239
00:15:00,130 --> 00:15:00,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About what?!</font>

240
00:15:00,940 --> 00:15:02,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's from my big sister.</font>

241
00:15:02,670 --> 00:15:09,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My dad, mom, sisters, brothers, 
nephews, nieces, and cousins...</font>

242
00:15:09,330 --> 00:15:12,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're all safe!</font>

243
00:15:12,220 --> 00:15:13,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

244
00:15:13,510 --> 00:15:19,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think they're near Octovern, 
though, so that's a bit worrying.</font>

245
00:15:19,550 --> 00:15:21,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

246
00:15:21,710 --> 00:15:26,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I did mention that I'm from 
a family of Worm tamers, right?</font>

247
00:15:26,220 --> 00:15:27,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never!</font>

248
00:15:27,870 --> 00:15:30,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can understand the Worms' language?</font>

249
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:33,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't understand it, no.</font>

250
00:15:33,400 --> 00:15:38,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But there's... something 
that comes across to me.</font>

251
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:45,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much!</font>

252
00:15:47,010 --> 00:15:50,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do they know you're here?</font>

253
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:52,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Worms can communicate 
their feelings instantly,</font>

254
00:15:52,890 --> 00:15:54,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">no matter how far away they are.</font>

255
00:15:54,920 --> 00:15:58,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their hearts resonate. 
My big brother told me so.</font>

256
00:15:58,330 --> 00:16:01,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or was it my sister?</font>

257
00:16:01,190 --> 00:16:04,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They resonate, huh? Oh... I remember.</font>

258
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:08,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The individuals are connected, right?</font>

259
00:16:10,530 --> 00:16:13,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, I'm glad your family is safe.</font>

260
00:16:13,490 --> 00:16:14,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

261
00:16:53,500 --> 00:16:58,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You still haven't told me what 
you're planning to do about Knives.</font>

262
00:17:01,390 --> 00:17:02,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll convince him to stop.</font>

263
00:17:02,790 --> 00:17:04,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You gotta be kidding.</font>

264
00:17:04,170 --> 00:17:05,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm serious.</font>

265
00:17:05,510 --> 00:17:08,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if I can't convince him, then...</font>

266
00:17:08,200 --> 00:17:10,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then what?</font>

267
00:17:10,040 --> 00:17:12,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can access plant cores.</font>

268
00:17:13,380 --> 00:17:17,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nai is also a plant, so I should be 
able to access his... I think.</font>

269
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:18,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And?</font>

270
00:17:19,350 --> 00:17:23,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My power as a plant is to take away.</font>

271
00:17:23,980 --> 00:17:28,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can get a hold of the plants Nai 
has taken in... and take them away.</font>

272
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:31,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Without the power of those plants,</font>

273
00:17:31,450 --> 00:17:35,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there's no way Nai can 
take down the whole fleet.</font>

274
00:17:35,090 --> 00:17:38,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. But will it work?</font>

275
00:17:38,910 --> 00:17:40,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you fail...</font>

276
00:17:40,780 --> 00:17:43,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and do Lost JuLai part two, 
that'd be bad.</font>

277
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:48,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Almost the entire planet's
 population is in Octovern.</font>

278
00:17:48,700 --> 00:17:52,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wipe them out, we're talking
the worst ending ever.</font>

279
00:17:56,140 --> 00:17:57,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

280
00:17:57,010 --> 00:18:01,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know. That's why, 
just to be safe, I want the Ark...</font>

281
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:07,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want Nai to be as far away 
from Octovern as possible. But...</font>

282
00:18:13,060 --> 00:18:16,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Resonance... That's it! Resonance!</font>

283
00:18:16,610 --> 00:18:17,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meryl?</font>

284
00:18:17,620 --> 00:18:21,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't you just let them 
know where you are?</font>

285
00:18:21,940 --> 00:18:27,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're a plant, maybe you 
can tell Knives your location.</font>

286
00:18:27,320 --> 00:18:29,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Similar to how the Worms are connected.</font>

287
00:18:29,150 --> 00:18:31,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about? 
How is that...</font>

288
00:18:32,990 --> 00:18:34,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that possible?</font>

289
00:18:34,500 --> 00:18:36,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I might be able to do it.</font>

290
00:18:36,150 --> 00:18:37,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?</font>

291
00:18:37,250 --> 00:18:39,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! And if we do that...</font>

292
00:18:39,750 --> 00:18:44,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We might be able to finish this without 
waiting for the immigrant fleet to arrive,</font>

293
00:18:44,790 --> 00:18:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or for Nai to show up at Octovern!</font>

294
00:18:47,010 --> 00:18:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Meryl.</font>

295
00:18:50,290 --> 00:18:55,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But even if I can tell Nai where I am...</font>

296
00:18:55,480 --> 00:18:56,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">will he come?</font>

297
00:18:56,760 --> 00:18:58,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course he will.</font>

298
00:18:58,510 --> 00:18:59,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wolfwood?</font>

299
00:19:00,080 --> 00:19:02,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter how bad you might be fighting,</font>

300
00:19:02,300 --> 00:19:07,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">big brothers always want to keep
 their little brothers close.</font>

301
00:19:08,190 --> 00:19:09,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nico...</font>

302
00:19:09,880 --> 00:19:13,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not talking about you! 
Just generally speaking.</font>

303
00:19:13,040 --> 00:19:14,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get it.</font>

304
00:19:14,090 --> 00:19:15,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't get shit!</font>

305
00:19:15,920 --> 00:19:18,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, where'll it be? 
Where do we want to lure him?</font>

306
00:19:19,420 --> 00:19:20,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a good spot.</font>

307
00:19:21,860 --> 00:19:23,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A place to settle this...</font>

308
00:19:31,960 --> 00:19:32,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

309
00:19:34,960 --> 00:19:38,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jessica, take care 
of the little kids, okay?</font>

310
00:19:38,110 --> 00:19:42,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will! And when you come back,
 I'll finally put this on your coat!</font>

311
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:45,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, kids, be good.</font>

312
00:19:45,940 --> 00:19:47,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good luck, Nico!</font>

313
00:19:47,060 --> 00:19:48,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care!</font>

314
00:19:48,170 --> 00:19:49,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be back soon!</font>

315
00:19:49,540 --> 00:19:51,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good luck, Livio!</font>

316
00:19:58,290 --> 00:20:01,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is all we've got.</font>

317
00:20:02,070 --> 00:20:07,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's better than nothing. I expect thanks.</font>

318
00:20:07,370 --> 00:20:08,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hey...</font>

319
00:20:08,640 --> 00:20:11,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The future is in your hands, 
Nicholas the Punisher.</font>

320
00:20:12,150 --> 00:20:15,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, Nicholas D. Wolfwood.</font>

321
00:20:16,450 --> 00:20:19,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't expect this from you.</font>

322
00:20:19,320 --> 00:20:25,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, thanks for letting us live.</font>

323
00:20:25,040 --> 00:20:28,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please come back alive.</font>

324
00:20:28,620 --> 00:20:31,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You still have a promise to fulfill.</font>

325
00:20:32,320 --> 00:20:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

326
00:20:34,140 --> 00:20:35,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't cry.</font>

327
00:20:35,230 --> 00:20:36,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not crying!</font>

328
00:20:36,650 --> 00:20:40,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't go taking this guys too seriously.</font>

329
00:20:40,600 --> 00:20:41,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's mean.</font>

330
00:20:41,970 --> 00:20:43,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quite uncalled for.</font>

331
00:20:43,040 --> 00:20:44,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, Wolfwood.</font>

332
00:20:44,990 --> 00:20:46,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really are too nice.</font>

333
00:20:50,800 --> 00:20:52,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to say, I didn't expect this.</font>

334
00:20:53,400 --> 00:20:57,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I assumed you'd be against 
me and Meryl coming along.</font>

335
00:20:57,770 --> 00:21:00,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How would I ever stop you?</font>

336
00:21:00,460 --> 00:21:02,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Point taken.</font>

337
00:21:02,160 --> 00:21:04,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, I was surprised, too.</font>

338
00:21:04,190 --> 00:21:05,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Same, actually.</font>

339
00:21:06,430 --> 00:21:10,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it is dangerous,
 so I'd prefer it if you weren't coming.</font>

340
00:21:10,520 --> 00:21:11,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

341
00:21:12,330 --> 00:21:14,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We want to help you carry it.</font>

342
00:21:14,590 --> 00:21:17,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not in this fight alone.</font>

343
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:21,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that look on your face?</font>

344
00:21:21,650 --> 00:21:23,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What <i>is</i> that look on your face?</font>

345
00:21:23,990 --> 00:21:25,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nothing.</font>

346
00:21:26,670 --> 00:21:31,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Meryl, Milly, I want you 
to promise me one thing.</font>

347
00:21:31,060 --> 00:21:32,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Promise?</font>

348
00:21:32,680 --> 00:21:35,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't do anything dangerous.</font>

349
00:21:35,900 --> 00:21:40,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course we won't. 
We have to leave a record.</font>

350
00:21:40,350 --> 00:21:43,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A record of all that's happened.</font>

351
00:21:43,600 --> 00:21:45,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Meryl...</font>

352
00:21:45,440 --> 00:21:46,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

353
00:21:48,820 --> 00:21:50,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh...</font>

354
00:21:50,410 --> 00:21:52,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good luck!</font>

355
00:21:52,920 --> 00:21:57,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good luck!</font>

356
00:21:57,920 --> 00:22:00,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come back in one piece!</font>

357
00:22:00,770 --> 00:22:03,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care, everyone!</font>

358
00:22:08,790 --> 00:22:10,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're off!</font>

359
00:23:51,180 --> 00:23:54,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, kill me! Kill a human!</font>

